node.text: Thank you guys so much for all the birthday well wishes and nice thoughts, especially the sexy pics of Robert Downey Jr, keep that business coming. My friend David made me a fabulous cake and I was lucky enough to celebrate with a ton of friends (thank u science 💉 ) including Kelly Link, @maureenjohnsonbooks and @blackholly. And, of course, Reginald. He didn’t get me a present but he did throw up in my shoe, and I say that counts! Xoxo Cassie

node.text: Hey guys! To celebrate the FIFTH ANNIVERSARY of The Dark Artifices, Simon and Schuster UK are issuing this gorgeous hardback anniversary edition of Lady Midnight. It will have a bonus story about Mark and Kieran in the Wild Hunt (“Stars to Burn”) and I’ve written you a letter about why I wrote TDA and what the setting means to me ;) Copies of the anniversary editions are available for pre order at Waterstones (check my profile) and will be in UK stores on September 2nd, 2021. Can you believe it’s been five years since we first went to the LA Institute?! 😇

node.text: Hello. Announcing a new project, SECRETS OF BLACKTHORN HALL. The link is in the image — pop over to the Tumblr to read the first update from Emma! SOBH takes place between TDA and The Wicked Powers. It follows the characters from Dark Artifices and delves into the history of those from The Last Hours when Julian and Emma have to travel to Blackthorn Hall and go through all the old papers and books. They find out something … or someone .. else might be sharing the space with them. They’ll also entertain visitors like Jem, Tessa, Cristina, Mark, Kieran, Kit, Ty, Dru and more. It’s a multimedia online project that will start updating every week on Monday starting August 16 — but the first post is already up, so check it out, enjoy, follow, and get ready for a year-long ride that’s free and fun. Tumble header art by @noverantale 😉 Enjoy! Xoxo Cassie 😘#shadowhunters #secretsofblackthornhall
